{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/asyiknya-chatting-dengan-pikachu-lewat-google-home/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Asyiknya Chatting dengan Pikachu Lewat Google Home","content":"<p>Guys, pernahkah kalian terbersit ingin mengobrol lama dengan Pokémon di kehidupan nyata? Jika memang iya, kayaknya kalian perlu deh mempertimbangkan untuk segera menggunakan perangkat Google Home. Karena di situ bakalan ada sebuah aplikasi yang memungkinkan kalian untuk berbicara dengan si maskot kuning yang super ikonik &#8220;Pikachu&#8221;.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_25541\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-25541\" data-attachment-id=\"25541\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/asyiknya-chatting-dengan-pikachu-lewat-google-home/attachment/isi-1-44/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/ISI-1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"(from : greatershepparton.com)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;(from : greatershepparton.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/ISI-1.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/ISI-1.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-25541\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/ISI-1.jpg\" alt=\"(from : greatershepparton.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-25541\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">(from : greatershepparton.com)</p></div>\n<p>Pada tanggal 1 November, The Pokémon Company mengumumkan bahwa mereka sedang mengembangkan aplikasi speaker cerdas yang disebut Pikachu Talk tahun ini di Jepang, yang memungkinkan pengguna Alexa, Beranda Google, dan Google Home Mini terlibat dalam obrolan seru dengan Pocket Monster yang paling terkenal itu. Tetapi untuk penggemar Pokémon di luar negeri, harus menunggu sedikit lebih lama yah karena aplikasi tersebut baru akan dirilis tahun 2018 mendatang.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_25544\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-25544\" data-attachment-id=\"25544\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/asyiknya-chatting-dengan-pikachu-lewat-google-home/attachment/isi-2-45/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/ISI-2.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"(from : europe-travel-guides.com)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;(from : europe-travel-guides.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/ISI-2.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/ISI-2.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-25544\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/ISI-2.jpg\" alt=\"(from : europe-travel-guides.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-25544\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">(from : europe-travel-guides.com)</p></div>\n<p>Cara untuk mengaktifkan aplikasi ini adalah dengan mengatakan &#8220;Pikachu, I Choose You&#8221; dan pada saat itu juga Pikachu akan mulai bercakap-cakap dengan kalian. Wuiihh kereeeen. Namun, The Pokémon Company mungkin harus meluncurkan penerjemah bahasa Pikachu sebelum penggemar dapat memahami respons tikus elektrik ini. Tidak seperti beberapa Pokémon yang bisa berkomunikasi dalam bahasa manusia, Pikachu hanya bisa membalas dengan ungkapan &#8220;pika pika&#8221; biasa di aplikasi ini.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_25547\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-25547\" data-attachment-id=\"25547\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/asyiknya-chatting-dengan-pikachu-lewat-google-home/attachment/isi-3-45/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/ISI-3.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"(from : europe-travel-guides.com)\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/ISI-3.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/ISI-3.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-25547\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/ISI-3.jpg\" alt=\"(from : europe-travel-guides.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-25547\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">(from : europe-travel-guides.com)</p></div>\n<p>Walaupun respons Pikachu terbatas, tetapi hal itu bukan berarti tidak ada maknanya. Pikachu bisa memberi tanggapan / jawaban seperti &#8220;Pikaaa,&#8221; &#8220;Pikapi,&#8221; dan &#8220;Pikachu,&#8221; tetapi kalian juga dapat berbicara dengan frasa kunci dengan berteriak &#8220;10.000.000 Volt Thunderbolt&#8221; untuk memicu respons khusus Pikachu agar mengeluarkan kekuatan listriknya. Hal ini pasti akan sangat menyenangkan bagi penggemar Pokemon di seluruh dunia.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_25550\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-25550\" data-attachment-id=\"25550\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/asyiknya-chatting-dengan-pikachu-lewat-google-home/attachment/isi-4-44/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/ISI-4.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"(from : europe-travel-guides.com)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;(from : europe-travel-guides.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/ISI-4.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/ISI-4.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-25550\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/ISI-4.jpg\" alt=\"(from : europe-travel-guides.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-25550\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">(from : europe-travel-guides.com)</p></div>\n<p>Selain itu, Pikachu Talk dirancang untuk segala umur. Hal ini tentu adalah sebuah ide yang cerdas mengingat banyaknya penggemar Pokémon yang sudah beranjak dewasa. Apilkasi ini dapat membuat mereka bernostalgia dengan karakter favorit pada zamannya. Oiya guys, kalian gak perlu repot-repot membuang uang untuk &#8220;Pikachu Talk&#8221; karena aplikasi ini benar-benar gratis.</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"22806f27-655c-571d-8cc8-10a4ecabfc25"}}}